es it well-suited for computational and mathematical sciences but less applicable to domains requiring physical experiments.\n\nIn essence, AlphaEvolve's requirement for automated evaluators makes it unsuitable for domains that depend on manual experimentation, physical testing, or human judgment in the evaluation process."],"durationSeconds":8.014224500000477,"searchCount":1},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"758bf7b6-eb4e-4465-b514-6d399bf02465","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/gg/Work/Yogi","sessionId":"d8d6b712-ec33-4776-a194-d9a72216a25f","version":"2.1.183","gitBranch":"main","slug":"bright-wondering-lantern"}
